title: Star Guardian Icon... it's been 10 days since I took the survey
body:
Test or survey whatever it is.

It's been more than a week and almost 10 days now.

I double checked by retaking the test on different computer.

Why am i not getting the icon?

replies.body: Since you've waited over a week on your specific issue, hit us up in a [support ticket](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new) so we cab assist you individually.  We'll be happy to help!
